{"tid":279172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★batman死左！","createTime":"2017-06-11T05:17:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-11T10:44:39.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"396f535bc912a4cc52af20ffef00fdbb624a895b","tid":279172,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T05:17:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170611/mobile/bkn-20170611092309411-0611_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170611%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170611092309411-0611_00862_001.html&d=J%2FdDR1h%2FRUzdpwiA6Y8oy0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=71effd08\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170611/mobile/bkn-20170611092309411-0611_00862_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n曾於劇集出演超級英雄「蝙蝠俠」一角的美國老牌男星Adam West於當地時間6月9日於洛杉磯因白血病離世，終年88歲，其家人翌日於社交網Facebook的官方帳戶及傳媒發聲明公布Adam死訊：「我們帶著極度的悲痛分享這個消息，Adam West勇敢對抗白血病一段短時間後，昨晚安然離世，他是個被愛的父親，丈夫、祖父及曾祖父，我們對他的思念難以言喻。我們知道你都將會掛念他，我們希望你知道你的愛與支持，多年來對他多有意義，今日好好擁抱你愛的人。」Adam家人另表示Adam不時當自己為光明的騎士，被揀中去向粉絲的生命作正面的影響，更講：「他永遠為我們的英雄！」"},{"pid":"9e40b2e702668213d33b9ba344059fac1bf52ade","tid":279172,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T05:18:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/11/131852_7db890df2dc015ad6bd8628a230c556f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F11%2F131852_7db890df2dc015ad6bd8628a230c556f.jpg&h=948036c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7480bb458fabb6c23a9a2cccc591b5569678369f","tid":279172,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T05:26:23.000Z","msg":"尋日就